{"lastModified":1768915856657,"uri":"c::32018258056::vessel::974804c0-1f8b-11f0-9305-8991174aa9d4","yachtType":["Sailing"],"description":"Operating Area: Trogir, Kaštela, Split\n\nAnother excellent yacht joined our fleet in Marina Baotić. Embark on a voyage of unparalleled luxury and exhilarating adventures aboard the Beneteau 54 “Eve One” Sailing Yacht. Immerse yourself in a world where cutting-edge design meets exceptional  performance, crafted to elevate your every nautical experience.\n\nStep into a realm of refined sophistication with the Beneteau 54 Sailing Yacht, where a recent interior and exterior upgrade has elevated its allure to unparalleled heights. The yacht now boasts an exquisitely redesigned interior that seamlessly blends modern aesthetics with timeless comfort. Each cabin is a haven of tranquility, adorned with luxurious details, while the saloon welcomes you with a sense of opulence that surpasses expectations.\n\nThe exterior of the Beneteau 54 stands as a testament to unique craftsmanship. With sleek lines and meticulously designed deck spaces, this yacht captures attention in every harbor. The upgraded exterior showcases a harmonious balance of form and function, ensuring that the Beneteau 54 not only looks distinctive but also performs with precision on the open waters. From its polished helm stations to the carefully selected materials throughout, the Beneteau 54 emanates an aura of exclusivity. Its unique design sets it apart in marinas worldwide, inviting admiration from seasoned sailors and newcomers alike. For those seeking a sailing experience that marries style with substance, the Beneteau 54 stands as a beacon of uniqueness, beckoning you to embark on a journey where every detail tells a tale of luxury and distinction.\n\nBook Your Sailing Dream\nIndulge in the extraordinary with the Beneteau 54 Sailing Yacht. Book your charter now and set sail towards a world of unmatched elegance, boundless horizons, and unforgettable moments at sea in Croatia. Your maritime adventure awaits.","blueprint":{"name":"EVE ONE","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::974804c0-1f8b-11f0-9305-8991174aa9d4::assets::801d0180-1f98-11f0-8515-1d653b032d5a/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::974804c0-1f8b-11f0-9305-8991174aa9d4::assets::b942d550-c9f9-11f0-b602-c1bbdeee17a7/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::974804c0-1f8b-11f0-9305-8991174aa9d4::assets::b942ae40-c9f9-11f0-b603-c1bbdeee17a7/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::974804c0-1f8b-11f0-9305-8991174aa9d4::assets::80430010-1f98-11f0-9f67-f1f2d6ab2698/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::974804c0-1f8b-11f0-9305-8991174aa9d4::assets::b9423910-c9f9-11f0-b602-c1bbdeee17a7/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::974804c0-1f8b-11f0-9305-8991174aa9d4::assets::80410440-1f98-11f0-8515-1d653b032d5a/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::974804c0-1f8b-11f0-9305-8991174aa9d4::assets::80423cc0-1f98-11f0-9f67-f1f2d6ab2698/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::974804c0-1f8b-11f0-9305-8991174aa9d4::assets::800b0020-1f98-11f0-a29c-e146f78ef3b1/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::974804c0-1f8b-11f0-9305-8991174aa9d4::assets::80410440-1f98-11f0-9f67-f1f2d6ab2698/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::974804c0-1f8b-11f0-9305-8991174aa9d4::assets::804263d0-1f98-11f0-8515-1d653b032d5a/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::974804c0-1f8b-11f0-9305-8991174aa9d4::assets::8040b620-1f98-11f0-a29c-e146f78ef3b1/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::974804c0-1f8b-11f0-9305-8991174aa9d4::assets::80437540-1f98-11f0-9f67-f1f2d6ab2698/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::974804c0-1f8b-11f0-9305-8991174aa9d4::assets::b942fc60-c9f9-11f0-b602-c1bbdeee17a7/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::974804c0-1f8b-11f0-9305-8991174aa9d4::assets::8038edf0-1f98-11f0-9f67-f1f2d6ab2698/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::974804c0-1f8b-11f0-9305-8991174aa